      "role": "interviewer",
      "text": "You mentioned \"Last time I switched banks was after Wells Fargo overdrew me…\" — that's helpful. Can you say more about friction with mobile deposit?"
    },
    {
      "role": "respondent",
      "text": "Chase's mobile deposit is fine but it holds $5K+ checks for 5 business days — that's when I curse."
    },
    {
      "role": "interviewer",
      "text": "You mentioned \"Chase's mobile deposit is fine but it holds $5K+ checks for …\" — that's helpful. Can you say more about opinion on fee transparency?"
    },
    {
      "role": "respondent",
      "text": "I want the fees on one page. Not buried in a 40-page PDF I can't search."
    },
    {
      "role": "interviewer",
      "text": "You mentioned \"I want the fees on one page. Not buried in a 40-page PDF I c…\" — that's helpful. Can you say more about willingness to switch to a challenger bank?"
